# Install Driver

## Resources

- https://www.rflink.nl/wires.php

## Nano

```
brew tap user/repo git@github.com:adrianmihalko/ch340g-ch34g-ch34x-mac-os-x-driver
brew cask install wch-ch34x-usb-serial-driver
```
